BUILD
===============
./autogen.sh
./configure --prefix=<dir>
make
make install

SETUP
==============
add:

export GTK_IM_MODULE=xim
export QT_IM_MODULE=xim
export XMODIFIERS=@im=fcitx
export XIM_PROGRAM=fcitx

to your ~/.bashrc

or you can use im-switch on some distos.

im-switch -s fcitx

RUN
=================
fcitx


Fcitx developer doc
=================
Please read doc/fcitx3.pdf (in S. Chinese).
Developer may want to read doc/Develop_Readme.GBK to get an overview of source code.
